      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know... i've called people before. but it doesn't change the fact that he's gone. it's not just a \"feeling\" i can talk my way out of. it feels like the world just lost its color and nothing is ever going to feel bright again. it feels like i'm just waiting for time to pass, but there's nothing to wait for. everything just feels so futile.",
